♪ Kaibigang hotdog, kaibigang
hotdog, kaibigang hotdog ♪

00:50:33.166 --> 00:50:37.875
♪ Kaibigang hot dog, kaibigang hot dog,
kaibigang hot dog ♪

00:50:48.250 --> 00:50:51.041
♪ Wala akong pera
